data.description: Move-in ready! Freshly renovated and ready for you! This charming brick ranch nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac offers convenience at your fingertips. Located mere minutes from shopping centers, restaurants, and Ft. Bragg, this home boasts tastefully refinished hardwood floors in the bedrooms complemented by new vinyl flooring in the kitchen formal dining room, bathrooms, and in the cozy family room featuring a fireplace. A recently refreshed interior showcases new paint throughout and a sleek granite countertop in the kitchen. Both bathrooms flaunt new vanities and fixtures. Bedrooms are generously sized, and the master bedroom features His & Her closets. Outside, a fenced backyard with a patio and a powered storage shed awaits. A single-car garage offers convenience.
